__________________________________________
He is seen eating lunch at a hotel.

We need you to Identify the fancy hotel where lunch is served with a view.

Flag Format: IntelHunt{HotelName}

Example: IntelHunt{Swissôtel}
__________________________________________

From the twitter account, you can find the post in which he post the image of the hotel where he is having lunch.
reverse searching this image using google image search engine for example would yield the location : 
Mövenpick Hotel and Residences Riyadh

so the flag is IntelHunt{Mövenpick}
